microlibc
=========

small experimentalish very-non-standard libc


build the library
-----------------

./configure
make
make test

build programs with it
----------------------

gcc/gccwrap myprogram.c -o myprogram





what works so far
-----------------
ctype
errno
stdint/inttypes
most of string.h
hsearch/bsearch/lsearch
qsort
strtol
small parts of stdio
most syscalls


what needs to be improved
-------------------------
malloc
your face
everything else
